{
  "stem": "17426.6",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I remember a good friend of mine, Russian, by the name of Boris, who was a inmate, because he tried to escape already from his [?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "D-- ?] from his [GERMAN] from his war camp or prisoner of war camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And he came in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And he said to me-- this was a Saturday.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He said, this afternoon when everybody is asleep-- there was a period where we slept between 2:00 and 4:00-- I am going to go over the fence.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I said, Boris, you're crazy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "You'll never make it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "You'll never make it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "The towers will see you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Some guard is gonna spot you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "You'll never make it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I will make it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I will make it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "He was very hopeful to make it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "He went to the other side.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And he was shot, was killed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "There were a number of lager blockalteste [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that were planning to escape by digging under one block to the outside.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "The story went that they were betrayed by one of those that were trying to escape.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I never was able to confirm this or deny this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "But the man who they-- was accused of that by those that supposedly knew was Goldstein.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "It was the same man who was in charge of the first aid room in Furstengrube, the first camp.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "He was the barber in-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Furstengrube-- who was in Steineck.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "He was the barber in Furstengrube, I should say.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Excuse me.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "I get confused sometime between those names.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And as I said, there's never been any confirmation.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "No one is [? know ?] for sure whether this happened or not.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Was I able to hide the gold?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was, but I had no purpose to.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was no reason for it.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
